{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "f075c7cc-eb30-4eb5-8250-bb8643cc6db8", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f075c7cc-eb30-4eb5-8250-bb8643cc6db8@1.pkg/1772597697999/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597699035", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f075c7cc-eb30-4eb5-8250-bb8643cc6db8@1.pkg/1772597697999/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597699035"}, "identifier": "f075c7cc-eb30-4eb5-8250-bb8643cc6db8", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>本题考查如何尊重并适应不同风格的老师。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>①：教师的教学风格各有不同，但在学习中，不同风格的老师都有值得我们学习的地方，我们必须主动适应不同教师的教学风格。故①正确</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>②：在学习中，不同风格的老师都有值得我们学习的地方，因此我们应该尊重欣赏，发现每位老师的独特价值。故②正确</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>③：&ldquo;忽视老师教学出现的问题&rdquo;说法错误，对于教师在教学中出现的问题，我们应当积极反馈，帮助教师改正错误，实现教学相长。因此③错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>④：&ldquo;尽力回避，反对风格并不契合的老师&rdquo;做法错误，对不同风格的教师，我们应当积极包容，而非盲目反对。因此④错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>①②正确，因此选A</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）南海区某中学的语文老师以严谨板书著称，历史老师擅长用粤剧案例讲解传统文化，数学老师常以游戏化教学激发兴趣。面对风格迥异的老师们，我们应该（ &nbsp; &nbsp;）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①承认差异，主动适应不同的教学方式</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>②尊重欣赏，发现每位老师的独特价值</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>③努力包容，忽视老师教学出现的问题</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>④尽力回避，反对风格并不契合的老师</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）南海区某中学的语文老师以严谨板书著称，历史老师擅长用粤剧案例讲解传统文化，数学老师常以游戏化教学激发兴趣。面对风格迥异的老师们，我们应该（    ）①承认差异，主动适应不同的教学方式②尊重欣赏，发现每位老师的独特价值③努力包容，忽视老师教学出现的问题④尽力回避，反对风格并不契合的老师", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f075c7cc-eb30-4eb5-8250-bb8643cc6db8@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754977893732", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①② &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①③ &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>②④ &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>③④</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify